set up config files at
********************
mysql 
/application/configs/application.ini
	set the following line
doctrine.dsn = "mysql://user:password@localhost/dbname"

upload path
/application/configs/config.php
	set the following
$PLACEWEB_CONFIG['uploadDir'] = "/var/www/place/public/content/";
	be sure this folder has write permissions for web user

Note all views are located in
/application/views/scripts
